---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="legal-content">
      <h2>Type of Information We Collect</h2>
<p>
GREAT GUS PRODUCTIONS LLC may collect personal information you voluntarily provide,
including your name, email address, and message content when you contact us.
We may also collect non-personal data such as browser type, device information,
and general site usage analytics.
</p>

<h2>How We Collect Information</h2>
<p>
Information is collected when you submit forms, send messages through our website,
or interact with site features. Payment transactions are handled entirely by
third-party providers and are not stored on our servers.
</p>

<h2>Why We Collect Information</h2>
<ul>
  <li>To respond to inquiries and provide customer support</li>
  <li>To operate and improve our website and services</li>
  <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
</ul>

<h2>Payments & Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>
All merchandise purchases are processed through Stripe and fulfilled by Printful.
Film streaming and digital access may be provided through Vimeo OTT.
GREAT GUS PRODUCTIONS LLC does not store credit card numbers or payment credentials.
</p>

<h2>We Do Not Sell Personal Information</h2>
<p>
GREAT GUS PRODUCTIONS LLC does not sell, rent, trade, or share personal information
for monetary or commercial purposes.
</p>
<p>
For transparency, we provide a link titled
<strong>“We Do Not Sell Personal Information.”</strong>
This link directs users to this Privacy Policy, which clearly explains our data practices.
No opt-out mechanism is required because we do not sell personal data.
</p>

<h2>Data Security</h2>
<p>
We take reasonable measures to protect personal information but cannot guarantee
absolute security. You provide information at your own risk.
</p>

<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>
This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page.
</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>
GREAT GUS PRODUCTIONS LLC<br />
Washington State<br />
<a href="mailto:greatgusproductions@gmail.com">
greatgusproductions@gmail.com
</a>
</p>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 1rem 6rem;
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .legal-content h2 {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .legal-content p,
  .legal-content li {
    color: #e6e6e6;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .legal-content ul {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }
</style>
